      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "内山坡羊",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "云黯黯，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "费贞娥上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山坡羊",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "但见烽烟笼罩，乱纷纷只见金鼓声喧闹。哭哀哀只见百姓们争先恐后，凄惨惨败兵退如潮。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "奴家费贞娥。自幼选入宫闱，奉国母娘娘恩厚，命我服侍公主，也曾伴读经书，略知君臣之礼。眼见金瓯破碎，社稷震摇，恨不能似男儿仗剑杀敌，报国捐躯，空怀一腔热血，徒付几声悲叹也！",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "天灾从天降，社稷已难保。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "王公公。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "费宫人，你怎么出宫来了？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "奉国母娘娘之命，出宫打听军情。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀费宫人哪，监军杜勋，竟大开城门，迎贼进城了！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "费贞娥"
      ],
      "text": "吖！如此速速奏明圣上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "走！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩、费贞娥同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "娘娘",
        "太子",
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀苦吓！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "娘娘、太子、公主同上，崇祯帝急上。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山坡羊",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "金鼓连天，海沸山崩顷刻间。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "娘娘"
      ],
      "text": "臣妾见驾。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀梓童吓！贼兵攻城，危在旦夕，眼见得邦家不能保全了。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
