    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "五供养",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "随朕到太庙中哭、哭告一番！领旨！告宗庙望先灵鉴昭，拜列圣英风未遥。啊呀，痛不肖承基不道。亡家国恨难保，倾社稷怨难消。啊呀帝室如悬磬，宫闱似覆巢，痛王家骨肉身难保。我也曾食旰衣宵，十七载王事辛劳。我也曾减刑又爆税，停乐不逍遥。盼只盼国富民有靠，谁料上天不佑保。风不顺雨不调，风不顺雨不调，上天不佑保，回首苍穹泪血空抛。啊呀不好了吓！啊呀陛下不好了！吓。天灾到，贼兵百万布城壕。那杜勋呢？他奸谋狡，启关迎寇长驱捣。啊呀！𠮾！虎贲龙骧呈散逃！休逆料，潜身逃遁须趁早。仓忙觅道，仓忙觅道。苍天哪，天！朝廷上下，分崩离析。勤王无师，立锥无地。朕惟有一死——",
      "text_length": 273
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "𠮾……",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，以谢天下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同哭",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "喂呀……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "我儿过来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太子"
      ],
      "text": "父王。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "可惜你生之不辰，罹遭国难。你可外穿民服，内藏玉牒，逃奔他乡，虽不指望你中兴，尚可继续宗祧。你速速改装，逃命去吧！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太子"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀父王吓！儿臣不肖，不能为国抒忠，以致国家沦亡，今日岂敢偷生逃遁。这生死——愿同一处的哟！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "唗！胡说，你欲同死，何益于事？若不逃往他处，必然绝灭宗祧，岂非天地间之大罪人吗？快去、快去、快去！",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "费贞娥陪太子同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀爱卿哪！当此国破家亡之际，可恨满朝文武各顾家身。今秉忠仗义，惟汝一人，你今保护太子逃命去吧！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "陛下。奴婢受陛下雨露深恩，粉身难报。今当保太子出宫潜藏僻静村庄，况太子生处无人厮认，奴婢当竭力保护，请万岁爷放心。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "卿乃大忠臣也。你……改装去吧！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩下，太子便装上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太子"
      ],
      "text": "父王，父王！啊呀！吓……",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "我儿，我儿！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同千秋岁",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝",
        "太子"
      ],
      "text": "泪如潮，此际心如搅，急嚷嚷逃奔荒郊。死別生离，死別生离，只索向海角天涯飘渺。离群雁生难料。覆巢卵谁能保？逃脱渔阳道。任潜踪匿迹，形影相吊。",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩拉太子同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "娘娘"
      ],
      "text": "我儿——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "静场。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "取酒来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "费贞娥取酒上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯帝"
      ],
      "text": "岁在甲申，暮春三月，大明气数，于厮尽矣！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902177",
      "scene_id": "70902177_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "父王母后啊！值此大难临身，微躯弱质何足为惜。请父王速将佩剑，立斩孩儿，父王也可放心矣！",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902177_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902177",
